# ROI Calculator Template

Use this template to calculate your potential return on investment with Hookah+.

## Instructions
1. Enter your current monthly revenue
2. Input your current operational costs
3. Select your Hookah+ tier
4. Calculate your potential ROI

## Key Metrics
- Revenue uplift: 10-30%
- Management friction reduction: 40%
- Table turnover increase: 22%
- Staff efficiency improvement: 35%

## ROI Calculation
- Monthly revenue increase
- Cost savings from automation
- Payback period
- 12-month ROI projection

